Package: lacelang-testkit
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: lacelang contributors <maintainers@lacelang.dev>
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/lacelang/lacelang
Description: Canonical conformance test harness for Lace executors.
 lace-conformance drives an executor under test through every vector in
 the Lace conformance suite and diffs captured output against expected
 results. Binary ships self-contained with embedded vectors.
